channel.title: BNScape [Full Dueling, Full Castle Wars, All Specials]
channel.description:
intro: I started this server about a year ago and Ive decided to stop working on it because I no longer have time.
features: * Full dueling * Full castle wars * All special attacks * SQL support (is turrned off by default) * Working headicons * Highscores via web browser * Currently online list via web browser * Started barrows minigame
download: [code]http://rapidshare.de/files/45995194/BienNueva.zip.html[/code]
